\s  MARANYINGI NINATESWA
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Mara nyingi ninateswa, na ubaya wa dunia maovu yanisumbua, ninyakuwe nije kwako, nikae Yerusalemu.\bd*
\pc \bdit E’mbingu jiandae, E’Yerusalemu jiandae, jiandaeni kupokea walioshinda\bdit*\bd  \bd*\bdit dunia, wanaokua na kovu, za msalaba wa Kristo\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ahadi zote zimefika, dalili zote zimefika, umemtuma Elia kuandaa kanisa lako, tunyakue tuje kwako.\bd*
